reviewText: not my fav show, but whatever floats your boat!
This series is fantastic - such fun and made me laugh from start to finish - I loved the extra's too! Really excellent viewing :)

This DVD Series arrived on time and was packaged perfectly. I have enjoyed many hours of entertainment from the young, beautiful and randy rich. I'm so sad that I I have to wait until Season 4 wraps up - April seems like a longtime away. I guess I'll start the Series all over again until then.

The product says DVD, implying it can be read by US DVD players, but it is NOT US compatible....so it either sits on my shelf unwatched or I have to purchase a new machine.  All other like products warn of the incompatibility, so it is unfortunate this merchant wasn't more forthcoming with product specs.
I saw one episode on the style channel and I was hooked. I wanted to start from the beginning. Can't stop watching. My friends are hooked too.
I had to get a multi-region dvd player for this and well worth it since Style network stopped airing the show for the moment
